name: CSA SINGLET
description:
Whoever says tanks aren’t happening nowadays is probably just someone who can’t pull of the look, the raw but fashionable look that the Serious Tank from Core Strength has to offer. Made out of 100% cotton without any annoying Rib Banding, the Serious Tank is perfect to show off your guns, shoulders and your general upper body mass and strength.

It is ARMS day every day when you wear the Serious Tank!

Sizing:

S - Width 46cm, Length 71cm
M - Width 51cm, Length 74cm
L - Width 56cm, Length 76cm
